>
>Billy:
>> Should I have them split this case to inspect cam/crank/innerds?
>
>I'd question whether you need to take the engine that far apart. I'd
probably just blast out the debris with an  air gun and possibly take off
one rod and check the condition of the bearing. If it looks good, I'd
